Deﬁnition of variables for reuse (Objective 1)
W3C endorsed ontologies
1 Ontologies whose URI is deﬁned in the http://www.w3.org/
namespace.
2 Ontologies identiﬁed by W3C as good ontologies.a Some of the
ontologies belonging to the list of good ontologies are FOAF, Dublin
Core, SIOC,b etc.
ahttps://www.w3.org/wiki/Good_Ontologies
bhttp://sioc-project.org/
Variable: percentage of LOV ontologies that reused W3C endorsed
ontologies.
